{
  "text": "The reduction over the squashed 5-sphere is consistent and forms a special case of dimensional reductions over squashed Sasaki-Einstein manifolds [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
  "correct_citation": {
